02:15:03.827 --> 02:15:05.467
growing and always learning.

02:15:05.747 --> 02:15:06.387
So I said, well, okay,

02:15:06.427 --> 02:15:07.287
I'll just go back to it.

02:15:07.868 --> 02:15:09.988
And when I went there and said, well,

02:15:10.029 --> 02:15:11.890
