02:15:18.171 --> 02:15:19.632
because who knows what we might learn.

02:15:20.332 --> 02:15:21.752
And then you run up and the first

02:15:21.773 --> 02:15:23.474
thing is annihilate the mother goddesses.

02:15:26.693 --> 02:15:28.074
why you never pull a Paul and take

02:15:28.095 --> 02:15:30.018
the verse out of context.

02:15:30.057 --> 02:15:30.377
Wow.

02:15:30.458 --> 02:15:31.900
At that point, I'm saying, okay, God,

02:15:32.041 --> 02:15:33.101
I know what we're going to be doing

02:15:33.122 --> 02:15:34.323
to show on as soon as we finish

02:15:34.363 --> 02:15:35.506
this Antichrist series.

02:15:36.466 --> 02:15:37.228
I know what we're doing.

02:15:37.248 --> 02:15:37.389
Yeah.

02:15:38.270 --> 02:15:38.510
Yeah.

02:15:39.649 --> 02:15:43.390
A little Natan from Yaffa Youth, Greg.

02:15:43.871 --> 02:15:44.631
Oh, what a thrill.

02:15:44.810 --> 02:15:46.252
Yeah, because, you know,

02:15:46.292 --> 02:15:48.512
when this thing burst up again,

02:15:48.533 --> 02:15:50.154
it is so many personal attacks on my

02:15:50.213 --> 02:15:50.493
wife.

02:15:50.533 --> 02:15:52.435
And it's so they're so revolting.

02:15:52.975 --> 02:15:55.376
And then all the personal asSha'uwlts on me

02:15:55.395 --> 02:15:58.117
and and their degradation of Yada Yahowah and

02:15:58.137 --> 02:16:00.217
the sites that they have put up just

02:16:00.257 --> 02:16:03.340
to degradate both of us and all of

02:16:03.399 --> 02:16:03.500
us.

