02:16:43.012 --> 02:16:44.272
Mike Tyson, George Foreman,

02:16:44.631 --> 02:16:46.052
first round knockout punch.

02:16:46.352 --> 02:16:46.753
Yep.

02:16:46.833 --> 02:16:47.933
And that's what he said.

02:16:47.994 --> 02:16:48.213
Okay.

02:16:48.234 --> 02:16:49.235
