02:16:59.420 --> 02:17:00.020
How was this?

02:17:00.040 --> 02:17:02.460
Amazing.

02:17:02.540 --> 02:17:02.881
I did.

02:17:04.121 --> 02:17:04.621
I think so.

02:17:04.682 --> 02:17:05.163
Okay.

02:17:05.183 --> 02:17:06.102
Yes.

02:17:06.143 --> 02:17:06.984
Score one for God.

02:17:07.004 --> 02:17:10.245
Okay.

02:17:10.305 --> 02:17:11.525
And that's why it's fun to do this.

02:17:13.379 --> 02:17:13.898
It really is.

